{"tid":606460,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"【Orage台】催眠閒聊 3 / EQ訓練器 5/ 3D暈 2 Day187 26/3","createTime":"2018-03-26T13:18:37.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-26T16:07:35.000Z","uid":122942,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"af2aab248c9a788ff6fac1ecb4e846f8b612cc5c","tid":606460,"uid":122942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-26T13:18:37.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://upload.cc/i2/5ADqP2.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi2%2F5ADqP2.gif&h=8c5a58f0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n大家好，我係Orage。 我會於每晚11點至2點開台玩遊戲同與觀眾聊天。<br />\n因為我極度3分鐘熱度，所以好少會一直玩同一隻Game。<br />\n有興趣嘅巴打入黎捧下場，一齊傾下計啦  <br />\n<br />\n今晚9點左右見 <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.twitch.tv/oragejan \" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.twitch.tv%2Foragejan%20&d=RsxxxD658N3gi6tisN0bb7%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=e374d56f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.twitch.tv/oragejan </a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i2/W4CK8P.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi2%2FW4CK8P.png&h=69cccb5f&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n另外我開左個FB專頁，有時會PO日常野同覺得有趣嘅事，<br />\n希望巴打們可以入黎比個讚。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/oragejan\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Foragejan&d=RsxxxD658N3gi6tisN0bb7%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=58efbf98\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/oragejan</a></div>"},{"pid":"fab90162ae63283edc2fe74f169cf63e23e11b41","tid":606460,"uid":122942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-26T13:20:16.000Z","msg":"已開<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a47c5534a4ccc04fac4ace0f770efd78a05da01","tid":606460,"uid":122942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-26T13:21:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ec3635932dbcefeb8e45c48c83ddf32435e04a3","ti